metadata.description:
Sincerity - Black pearl #1

Black pearl – a collection of 10 female characters that embody all the qualities that make woman a woman, that we love and appreciate. Strength and sincerity, sexuality and modesty, self-confidence and justice... 

Inspired by life…

Buyer receives also original file 1700x1500 px
